data.description: If you're looking for a lovely 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home in the heart of the downtown San Antonio area, look no further! This home has mature trees in both the front and backyards optimal for enjoying outdoor living in style. If you're looking for an open-style living concept with the living room, dining area and kitchen connected, this home is the one! Close to major employers, downtown area universities and connectivity to major freeways, don't miss out on the opportunity to own this amazing home. Make an appointment to stop in and see this home! There's also an assumable loan (First-Time HomeBuyer Assistance) Loan at 3.375%!
